title: Creepy Archives V1-10
description:
Volumes 1-10 of Creepy Archives
Dark Horse Archives, 2008-2011

Vol. 1, issues 1-5, 253 pages
Vol. 2, issues 6-10, 297 pages
Vol. 3, issues 11-15, 288 pages
Vol. 4, issues 16-20, 242 pages
Vol. 5, issues 21-25, 234 pages
Vol. 6, issues 26-32, 298 pages
Vol. 7, issues 33-36, 258 pages
Vol. 8, issues 37-41, 312 pages
Vol. 9, issues 42-45, 258 pages
Vol. 10, issues 46-50, 281 pages

Contributors include Frank Frazetta, Al Williamson, Alex Toth, Jack Davis, Archie Goodwin, Russ Jones, Joe Orlando, Steve Ditko, Bernie Wrightson, Wallace Wood, Gene Colan, Ron Parker, Carl Wessler, Gil Kane, Dick Giordano and about two truckloads of other people.

As with the Eerie Archives, there's not really much to say about these books. They're classics, responsible for helping shape several generations of comic book people who were influenced and inspired by them. Here you find them in digital archive editions, looking as good as I've ever seen them.
